# Enforce LF in the working tree for all text files, regardless of the
# contributor's core.autocrlf setting. Without this, Git checks files out as
# CRLF on Windows (autocrlf=true) and Biome's LF formatter fails the verify
# gate — making the gate non-deterministic across checkouts.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
